<h2 class="header">Meth</h2>
<div id="math-content">
    <div id="calc-div">
        <div id = "calc" class="z-depth-1">
            <div id = "input-output">
                <div id = "input">hamsters</div>
                <div id = "output">0</div>
            </div>
            
            <div id = "algorithms">
                <a class="btn disabled">*</a>
                <a class="btn disabled">/</a>    
                <a class="btn disabled">-</a>
                <a class="btn disabled">+</a>
                
               <a class="waves-effect waves-light btn-large ac-button" onclick={allClear()}>AC</a>
            </div>
            
            <div id = "integers">
                <a class="btn-floating btn-large waves-effect waves-light red" onclick={zero()}>0</a>
                <a class="btn-floating btn-large waves-effect waves-light red" onclick={one()}>1</a>
                <a class="btn-floating btn-large waves-effect waves-light red" onclick={two()}>2</a>
                <a class="btn-floating btn-large waves-effect waves-light red" onclick={three()}>3</a>
                <a class="btn-floating btn-large waves-effect waves-light red" onclick={four()}>4</a>
                <a class="btn-floating btn-large waves-effect waves-light red" onclick={five()}>5</a>
                <a class="btn-floating btn-large waves-effect waves-light red" onclick={six()}>6</a>
                <a class="btn-floating btn-large waves-effect waves-light red" onclick={seven()}>7</a>
                <a class="btn-floating btn-large waves-effect waves-light red" onclick={eight()}>8</a>
                <a class="btn-floating btn-large waves-effect waves-light red" onclick={nine()}>9</a>
            </div>
            
            <div id="switch-div">
                <a id="switch-button" class="waves-effect waves-light btn indigo lighten-2" onclick={switchButton()}>Switch to Human Calculator</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div id="calc-2" class="z-depth-1">
            <form name="calc">
                <input id="input-2" name="input" placeholder="0">
                <br>
                <input id="times" class="btn disabled" type="button" value="*" onclick="document.calc.input.value+='*'">
                <input id="divide" class="btn disabled" type="button" value="/" onclick="document.calc.input.value+='/'">
                <input id="minus" class="btn disabled" type="button" value="-" onclick="document.calc.input.value+='-'">
                <input id="plus" class="btn disabled" type="button" value="+" onclick="document.calc.input.value+='+'">
                <input class="btn" type="button" value="AC" onclick="ac()">
                <br>
                <input class="btn-floating btn-large waves-effect waves-light red" type="button" value="0" onclick="num0()">
                <input class="btn-floating btn-large waves-effect waves-light red" type="button" value="1" onclick="num1()">
                <input class="btn-floating btn-large waves-effect waves-light red" type="button" value="2" onclick="num2()">
                <input class="btn-floating btn-large waves-effect waves-light red" type="button" value="3" onclick="num3()">
                <br>
                <input class="btn-floating btn-large waves-effect waves-light red" type="button" value="4" onclick="num4()">
                <input class="btn-floating btn-large waves-effect waves-light red" type="button" value="5" onclick="num5()">
                <input class="btn-floating btn-large waves-effect waves-light red" type="button" value="6" onclick="num6()">
                <input class="btn-floating btn-large waves-effect waves-light red" type="button" value="7" onclick="num7()">
                <br>
                <input class="btn-floating btn-large waves-effect waves-light red" type="button" value="8" onclick="num8()">
                <input class="btn-floating btn-large waves-effect waves-light red" type="button" value="9" onclick="num9()">
                <input class="btn-floating btn-large waves-effect waves-light red" type="button" value="." onclick="dot()">
                <input class="btn-floating btn-large waves-effect waves-light red" type="button" value="=" onclick="equal()">
            </form>
            <div id="switch-div-2">
                <a id="switch-button-2" class="waves-effect waves-light btn indigo lighten-2" onclick={switchButton2()}>Switch to Hamster Calculator</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <p id="math-info">
        Long ago, when humans didn't exist, hamsters were known as the superior creatures that dominated this world.
        Their intellect far surpassed any creature ever createdâ”€even humans.
        They were like alien beings with sophisticated technology that can never be developed by mere humans.
        Unlike humans from the present, hamsters coexisted with dinosaurs, inluding the tyrannosaurus rex and velociraptor.
        Though, dinosaurs weren't a threat to the hamsters; they were friendly creatures towards their elite.
        <br>
        <br>
        A year after, hamsters invented their first calculator.
        It was as equivalent as the modern calculator made by humans but far more advanced.
        To the left is a sample of the sophisticated calculator made by hamsters.
    </p>
</div>
